Act 704 of the Regular Session
Act 704 of the Regular Session
1 State of Arkansas
A Bill
2 95th General Assembly
3 Regular Session, 2025 SENATE BILL 562
4
5 By: Senator Hill
6 By: Representative Holcomb
7
For An Act To Be Entitled
8
9 AN ACT TO AMEND THE LAW CONCERNING THE OFFICE OF
10 INTERNAL AUDIT; TO REPEAL THE REQUIREMENT FOR AN
11 ANNUAL PROJECT REVIEW AND EFFICIENCY STUDY OF THE
12 ARKANSAS DEPARTMENT OF TRANSPORTATION; AND FOR OTHER
13 PURPOSES.
14
15
Subtitle
16
17 TO AMEND THE LAW CONCERNING THE OFFICE
18 OF INTERNAL AUDIT; AND TO REPEAL THE
19 REQUIREMENT FOR AN ANNUAL PROJECT REVIEW
20 AND EFFICIENCY STUDY OF THE ARKANSAS
21 DEPARTMENT OF TRANSPORTATION.
22
23 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
24
25 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code ยง 25-43-1004(e)(5), concerning the powers of
26 the Office of Internal Audit, is repealed.
27 (5)(A) Conduct an annual project review and efficiency study of
28 the Arkansas Department of Transportation, including without limitation a
29 review of processes, procedures, procurement, projects, appeals, and
30 expenditures.
31 (B) The results of the study under subdivision (e)(5)(A)
32 of this section shall be reported to the Legislative Council no later than
33 October 1 of each year with the first report to be submitted on or before
34 October 1, 2023; and
35 APPROVED: 4/16/25
36
